<p>11(17): p. 3829-3834. </p>
<p>[2]Sorokowska, A., et al., Food-Related Odors Activate Dopaminergic Brain Areas. </p>
<p>Frontiers in Human Neuroscience, 2017. 11: p. 625. </p>
<p>[3]Ferreri, L., et al., Dopamine modulates the reward experiences elicited by music. </p>
<p>Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences, 2019. 116(9): p. 3793. </p>
