➜饭圈用复制粘贴和乱码，占领了豆瓣的评论区
http://www.sohu.com/a/434972182_260616	35591
<div id="sohuplayer">
<script type="text/javascript" src="//tv.sohu.com/upload/swf/showVrsPlayer.js"></script>
